~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
version 1.0
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Initial release of PhantomWatch.
* Real-time monitoring of network traffic.
* Detection and alerting for suspicious activities.
* Integration with external threat intelligence sources.
* User-friendly CLI interface
* Comprehensive logging and reporting features.
* Performance benchmarks:
    * Monitored 5000 events: Previously 5m 30s / Now 1m 15s
    * Processed 10000 events: Previously 12m / Now 3m 40s